{"tid":1660171,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"涉以網名「金正恩」呼籲網民包圍新屋嶺 地盤工被控獲准保釋","createTime":"2019-10-17T10:59:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T11:22:51.000Z","uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"600d00230a22e543152333d627c8c53f23524a90","tid":1660171,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T10:59:01.000Z","msg":"警方昨於葵涌邨旭葵樓拘捕一名地盤工，指他涉於9月在網上社交媒體發放失實言論，指警方曾打死被拘留者，並煽動他人包圍新屋嶺扣留中心。地盤工人被控一項煽惑他人非法集結罪，案件今於西九龍法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191017/large/1571290175_8f40.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191017%2Flarge%2F1571290175_8f40.jpg&h=0d7f0861&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據悉，被告潘榕偉（36歲）以網名「金正恩」，於<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">公開群組</span></strong></span>發佈警方曾把被拘留者虐打致死的言論，並呼籲網民包圍新屋嶺扣留中心。<br />\n<br />\n被告暫毋須答辯，控方要求押後案件，以待警方進一步調查，並不反對被告保釋。主任裁判官羅德泉將案押後至11月28日再訊，被告獲准以1,000元保釋，另須遵守不得離港及每周到警署報到一次等條件，而被告保釋期間不得發放任何煽動暴力的資訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n被告被控一項煽惑他人非法集結，指他於9月期間在香港煽惑身份不詳的人，參與非法集結，即於新屋嶺扣留中心外集結。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：WKCC3932/19】<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191017/60163913\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191017%2F60163913&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAR6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=e50251bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191017%2F60163913&h=788741bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191017/60163913</a>"},{"pid":"c8bbec3def1195ce6d5e3d260a88b97e4be72a8a","tid":1660171,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T11:00:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eD1QUeo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeD1QUeo.jpg&h=564aedde&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"803685f78443f9bc44d834b7f2f3df91b5de3e85","tid":1660171,"uid":43276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T11:02:56.000Z","msg":"Tg公海? Mon po 狗？"},{"pid":"90a5ab63ef27427e11c65e08f99f740200e9c694","tid":1660171,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"803685f78443f9bc44d834b7f2f3df91b5de3e85","tid":1660171,"uid":43276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T11:02:56.000Z","msg":"Tg公海? Mon po 狗？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T11:04:22.000Z","msg":"Fab"},{"pid":"eb7821e96957f2a93fb7800ec560d9ae467485e6","tid":1660171,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T11:08:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dee531da2ef4219430a84c551458e2f8684f219f","tid":1660171,"uid":5289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T11:09:24.000Z","msg":"文字獄"},{"pid":"f7098cd12976f39d6bc3c76c812cc31dae8ef32f","tid":1660171,"uid":293698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T11:10:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb8df29ec51e5cb2c379986fc42b4eeeefbfacab","tid":1660171,"uid":224561,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T11:11:00.000Z","msg":"全世界都話警犬打死人淨係拉佢一個<br />\n叫人圍狗屋條八婆又唔拉<br />\n<br />\n所以係咪金仔見到好嬲然後想拉人?"},{"pid":"7d1fd613343b91f7aee3a1bebbdb28aa3bd25dec","tid":1660171,"uid":110125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T11:15:12.000Z","msg":"姐係叫金正欣 习近遠果啲會好危險？"},{"pid":"fb0c9ed925083dfde2c8e6ac4259af11c2a06453","tid":1660171,"uid":110125,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7d1fd613343b91f7aee3a1bebbdb28aa3bd25dec","tid":1660171,"uid":110125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci